      "effect": "Cannot be Normal Summoned/Set. Must first be Special Summoned (from your hand) by Tributing 1 \"Sanga of the Thunder\", \"Kazejin\", and \"Suijin\"."
    },
    "fr": {
      "name": "Gardien de la Porte",
      "effect": "Ni Invocable Normalement ni Posable Normalement. Doit d'abord \u00eatre Invoqu\u00e9e Sp\u00e9cialement (depuis votre main) en Sacrifiant 1 \"Sanga du Tonnerre\", \"Kazejin\" et \"Suijin\"."
    },
    "de": {
      "name": "Torw\u00e4chter",
